{"tid":2393155,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇2月5號上唔到$800、段永平就賺3百萬？","createTime":"2021-02-03T09:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T09:15:35.000Z","uid":182610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49a39643826be0ec5575c5bb1d0a30f348c69c49","tid":2393155,"uid":182610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"段永平：已做空遊戲驛站<br />\n<br />\n1月30日，段永平稱賣出了100個800美金裸callGME的期權，權利金在40美金左右。<br />\n<br />\n這裏大概的操作就是，段永平要在賭博。在賭這週五，也就是在2月5日，GME的股價到不了800美金。<br />\n<br />\n因為如果沒有到達800美金，其買入該期權的人就不會行權，段永平能收益每股40多美金的權利金，一張期權是100股，也就是4000美金的收益，而段永平賣了100張，也就是收益四十多萬美金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.futunn.com/hk/post/8677323?src=7&amp;seo_redirect=1&amp;level=1&amp;data_ticket=640046df4deb862c72138aa081adb712&amp;utm_medium=futu_niuniu_share&amp;utm_content=web_share&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;utm_term=8677323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.futunn.com%2Fhk%2Fpost%2F8677323%3Fsrc%3D7%26seo_redirect%3D1%26level%3D1%26data_ticket%3D640046df4deb862c72138aa081adb712%26utm_medium%3Dfutu_niuniu_share%26utm_content%3Dweb_share%26utm_campaign%3Dnews%26utm_term%3D8677323&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjZ0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=4ceea8c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.futunn.com/hk/post/8677323?src=7&amp;seo_redirect=1&amp;level=1&amp;data_ticket=640046df4deb862c72138aa081adb712&amp;utm_medium=futu_niuniu_share&amp;utm_content=web_share&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;utm_term=8677323</a>"},{"pid":"ae216b3b8c1c449dc56d9a1cece3ccf0c9fbeab4","tid":2393155,"uid":182610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"SH 撚快啲夾死佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815f00ca31df007fa67bdb4466b9e701795bae99","tid":2393155,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02